	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello I am a wizard of the 52lvl and I find that it is best to port only those are in your guild and those that can help you when u need it.In pvp the only way to kill someone is when they dont see you dont root them it dont work ,only on mobs kite melee and stay out of range of casters when they get in range use your fastest hitting dd then move out of range again,stick and move.&nbsp;&nbsp;I love my wizard she rocks when she is fighting my problem is i cant wait for the tanks to aggro them but when we have to many I blast then I root and back up and let them take the mob. If you get caught at spires gate then use dispell it will take of the dots if you are poisioned have a potion of find a cleric you will live. Spurt is a wizards worst enemy if you get your gate of nullify spell over and over again. I have lived threw it many times it does work so remeber to do that if you get spurted. Dont shut done come or exit you will lose exp if u do just dispell and will live to say I lived threw a spurt attack. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
