	   <tr><td colspan=2>I think Wizards are a great class (and for more than raising money from ports to twink new characters).&nbsp;&nbsp;The Wizards role in a group is as a shock tropper.  We just can't hold a candle to the amount of damage a tank can do over the long haul, but we can lay down a tremendous amount of damage quickly.  <br>For a group, this usually means you only nuke a mob once if there are enough tanks to deal with it.  We really come into play when there are multiple mobs.  We can help a tank kill a mob in a 3rd of the normal time and still avoid agros if played carefully.  We also should focus on gunning down mobs that are nearly dead and running for help.  That is just my 2 cents worth on wizards.  I just wish we could make others see what we really do.  It would be nice if others could see the damage we do instead of the message 'The gnoll is hit with a blast of frost'. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
