	   <tr><td colspan=2>After 20 the 2 areas I've found to be most productive has been Highhold Keep fighting goblins and Lake of Ill Omen/Frontier Mountains.&nbsp;&nbsp;Highhold Keep is nasty close fighting in a confined space. I really makes you be judicious in what DD spells you cast: too much damage and the aggro on you ALL the time.<br><br>I really Like LOIO/FM. The Lake is great for soloing and grouping hunting a variety of critters. Frontier Mountains is my first taste of giant slaying and I really get a rush seeing those big oafs falling over.... again and again and again.<br><br>I'll level 27 now and expect these areas to keep me occupied  past the level 30 plateau.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
