	   <tr><td colspan=2>With my Wizard i haven't spend _any_ points in spell schools neither in weapons skills.<br>It will go up slower in the beginning, but it will raise. Save your points for something else, Bind Wounds is good to have (the only possibility to heal yourself), trading skills or later for research (lvl16). Sense Heading will be maxed if you hotkey it and hit it during fights permanently. IMO it is not necessary to waste training points for spell/melee skills.<br><br><br>Fumadyen, 9th season soloing Wizard<br>Solusek Ro Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
